					p(class="title__name") Contact us
					p(class="title__description") 班傑明．摩爾 (台灣)
				div(class="section__heading") 大直旗艦店
				div(class="section__text") 
					ul(class="information")
						li(class="information__text")
							|104台北市中山區敬業一路128巷39號
							a(class="information__alone" href="https://www.google.com.tw/maps/place/10491%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E5%8D%80%E6%95%AC%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF128%E5%B7%B739%E8%99%9F/@25.0834487,121.5513601,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x3442ac1192e23793:0x3bd81403f61fab2a!8m2!3d25.0834487!4d121.5535488" target="_blank")
								i(class="information__icon fa fa-map-marker" aria-hidden="true")
						li(class="information__text") 0800-627-000
						li(class="information__text") Email:bm@sensedesign.com.tw
						li(class="information__text")
							a(class="information__link" href="https://www.facebook.com/benjaminmooretaiwan/" target="_blank")
								i(class="information__icon fa fa-facebook-official" aria-hidden="true")
								span(class="information__fanspage") 班傑明摩爾粉絲團
						li(class="information__text")
							a(class="information__link" href="https://www.instagram.com/benjaminmooretaiwan/" target="_blank")
								i(class="information__icon fa fa-instagram" aria-hidden="true")
								span(class="information__fanspage") 班傑明摩爾instagram
